{"tid":2406794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬警開槍鎮壓抗爭 拘350人","createTime":"2021-02-13T13:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T14:29:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d87e7bd2b55d42abc1d054060e8d15862d40fcfd","tid":2406794,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:40:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210213/STPKTGYNB5CNPM3NTYBBDT4YEA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210213%2FSTPKTGYNB5CNPM3NTYBBDT4YEA%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ2aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=a863bc3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210213%2FSTPKTGYNB5CNPM3NTYBBDT4YEA%2F&h=58907c22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210213/STPKTGYNB5CNPM3NTYBBDT4YEA/</a><br />\n<br />\n緬警開槍鎮壓抗爭 拘350人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HO7r_PhfUr-wJkg3IqAK3S6N388=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5M4PZY3S45FZ5HTLM3YY7L35XQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHO7r_PhfUr-wJkg3IqAK3S6N388%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5M4PZY3S45FZ5HTLM3YY7L35XQ.jpg&h=cc31a343&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■持槍警員在毛淡棉拘捕反政變示威者。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸本月1日軍事政變並軟禁資政昂山素姬後，全國抗爭至昨日已屆一星期，其中第四大城市毛淡棉有警開槍鎮壓致三傷，累計350人被拘留；<span class=\"orange\">同時被華府制裁的敏昂萊政府，釋放了兩萬多名囚犯，團體擔心這是為「預位」給大批政治犯。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n監獄放兩萬人 恐留位予政治犯<br />\n<br />\n根據紅十字會消息，開槍事件在東南部城鎮毛淡棉發生，在抗爭早期，當地警員已施放催淚彈對付和平群眾。按自由電台亞洲昨拍到片段，警員朝數以萬計靜坐人群推進，其間抓着一個男子，迎頭就打；示威者擲石還擊，警察於是開槍。目擊者說至少三人受傷，其中兩男子分別傷了面頰和手臂，女子則是腹部位置中槍，另五人被捕。然而槍擊未成功驅散人群，「人越聚越多」。<br />\n<br />\n其他地方亦有各項罷工示威，在最大城市仰光，數百名醫護人員穿了白袍遊行經過佛教聖地大金寺，另一邊廂就有一批足球迷穿球衣遊行，手持幽默標語譴責軍方，例如「我討厭軍方更甚於曼聯」。首都內比都、海岸城鎮達韋及北部邦會密支那都有示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n對於人民用腳表態，被美國列入緬甸軍政府10人制裁名單的總統敏昂萊，昨日呼籲各界為國家利益盡快重返崗位；同日政府趁住公眾假期，特赦23,000多名囚犯，關注團體估計當中包括20名早前被拘留的示威者，但不包括昂山素姬等政要，此舉反而令團體擔心官方是要清空爆滿監獄，準備囚禁政治犯。據聯合國人權辦公室昨日估計，軍事政變後有逾350人被拘留，包括官員、社運成員和僧侶，部份人面臨的刑事控罪「理據成疑」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，鑑於軍方政變後不斷發放有利自己的假消息，在緬甸流行的社交網平台facebook宣佈會減少軍方戶口圖文的觸及率。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I2PxkwqfjlllBouNDO5849yl08U=/1775x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A6XNIRJ5KRFWBJ4GVX3VJEMPBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI2PxkwqfjlllBouNDO5849yl08U%3D%2F1775x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA6XNIRJ5KRFWBJ4GVX3VJEMPBE.jpg&h=61e37cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民眾身塗彩繪在中國駐仰光使館外抗議政變。"},{"pid":"4c5caf207d03d2b156b626d339999346ddd3d164","tid":2406794,"uid":82640,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"殺人獲釋<br />\n示威坐監<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acbaa9bc78243b71497032ba5fb5912d0e1a223f","tid":2406794,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"有咩問題？"},{"pid":"634e1e61c33538538760fca762ab8b527bc9aa92","tid":2406794,"uid":143383,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"我有個緬甸朋友，上年先屌香港示威者收美國佬錢。<br />\n前幾日見佢，就話明點解香港人咁憎中國、咁憎習近平。<br />\n之後狂屌幾個鐘話軍政府收中國錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{